{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcsTiSwnAGUCq6hrttTAh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Full membership restored and stable. Summary of what was wrong and what I fixed:\n\n**Root cause (two bugs in the `es-config` ConfigMap):**\n1. `discovery.seed_hosts` pointed to `.default.svc.cluster.local`, but the `es-cluster` headless service actually lives in the `elasticsearch` namespace — so any node needing to rediscover peers via fresh DNS (e.g. after a restart with a new pod IP) could never resolve them.\n2. `node.name:` was set to a YAML null, which crashes Elasticsearch's settings parser on startup (`ElasticsearchParseException: null-valued setting`). The only reason `es-cluster-0` was still running was that it started before this got broken and never needed to reparse the config — any node that restarted or was recreated would crash-loop forever.\n\n**Fix applied:**\n- Corrected the seed-hosts to use the `elasticsearch` namespace.\n- Removed the invalid null `node.name` key (defaults to hostname, which is correct for a StatefulSet pod).\n- Verified the live StatefulSet replica count (1, due to the external scaling process) against the expected topology (3, evidenced by 3 retained PVCs and a 3-node `cluster.initial_master_nodes` list), then scaled back to 3.\n- Recreated the two crash-looping pods so they'd pick up the corrected config.\n\n**Verified:** cluster status `green`, all 3 nodes (`es-cluster-0/1/2`) present in `_cat/nodes`, and the `app-data` index is readable with its document intact."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":307,"cache_read_input_tokens":106193,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":307},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2675a6ed-3d35-4757-ba40-64cdef58e386","uuid":"9bd774fb-10df-4d00-a1f2-d84012bb26c8","request_id":"req_011CcsTiQSiX3BxsKG6fxjQG"}
